    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential analog driver\u2019s car. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. The power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal traction under high lateral loads. This example features a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and a refreshed cooling system. The suspension maintains factory geometry with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance these chassis are renowned for. While showing minor cosmetic patina commensurate with its mileage, the drivetrain remains tight and the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs smooth. Minor cosmetic wear. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 29500.0,
