    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i finished in elegant Space Gray Metallic. This luxury SUV offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep gloss, though a few minor stone chips are visible on the front fascia from standard highway driving. Inside, the Canberra Beige Dakota leather interior is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; while there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the cabin remains a serene, premium environment. Equipped with a 3.0L TwinPower Turbo engine, this vehicle has been serviced regularly, including a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. High-end features include a panoramic sunroof, heated front seats, a crisp navigation system, and a high-resolution backup camera. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced within the last 5,000 miles. It drives smoothly with the signature BMW responsiveness you expect. This is a solid, reliable vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
